flag in the
city after government troops
retook its center.

05:29.229 --> 05:32.432 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HAIDER AL-ABADI, Iraqi Prime
Minister (voice-over):
ISIS said they would fight in
Ramadi, but

05:32.465 --> 05:36.403 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
