fight. They
fled, and many of them were
killed.

05:36.436 --> 05:41.808 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MARGARET WARNER: It was a
seven-month slog
to this day. Islamic State
militants had captured

05:41.841 --> 05:47.847 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Ramadi, capital of the majority
Sunni Anbar
province, in May.

05:47.881 --> 05:53.753 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
