weeks, last week,
Iraqi forces, backed by U.S.-led
coalition

05:53.787 --> 05:59.092 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
airstrikes, finally launched an
assault into
the city. And over the weekend,
they made

05:59.125 --> 06:03.797 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
a final push to seize its
central administration
complex.

06:03.830 --> 06:09.736 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Yesterday, troops celebrated as
they raised
the Iraqi flag above the key
government building.

06:09.769 --> 06:15.709 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
