06:17.877 --> 06:19.913 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
COL. STEVE WARREN, U.S.
Spokesman for Operation
Against ISIS: I would agree that
probably

06:19.946 --> 06:25.085 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
