it's just
going to get only more
difficult.

10:33.299 --> 10:38.238 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
GWEN IFILL: Matt Bradley
reporting for us
tonight from Baghdad for The
Wall Street Journal,

10:38.271 --> 10:40.507 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
