for the trial.

22:51.537 --> 22:57.509 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
So far, there are 1, 500
volunteers. He is
carefully watching them for side
effects.

22:57.543 --> 22:59.411 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
So far, so good.

22:59.445 --> 23:06.252 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DR. MARK KIEH: Those we have
seen are expected
side effects of fever, muscle
pain, pain at

23:06.285 --> 23:13.225 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
the injection sites, some joint
pain, some
-- few people with rashes that
resolve over

23:13.259 --> 23:15.127 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
time.

23:15.160 --> 23:19.565 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MILES O'BRIEN: The trial is run
