Ministry of Health and the U.S.
National Institute

23:19.598 --> 23:21.800 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
of Allergy and Infectious
Disease.

23:21.834 --> 23:28.040 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
