23:28.073 --> 23:29.842 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DR. ANTHONY FAUCI, Director,
National Institute
of Allergy and Infectious
Diseases: At least

23:29.875 --> 23:35.347 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
