23:37.149 --> 23:41.787 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MILES O'BRIEN: On March 14,
2015, he suited
up to treat a U.S. health care
worker who

23:41.820 --> 23:47.926 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
