intensive
care possible. It kept him alive
while his

23:53.299 --> 23:56.135 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
body mounted its own defense.

23:56.168 --> 23:58.704 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
It was touch and go for a week,
