23:58.737 --> 24:04.109 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DR. ANTHONY FAUCI: All of the
people who have
recovered from Ebola, even those
who have

24:04.143 --> 24:10.482 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
been very ill, it was their
immune system
that ultimately suppressed and
eliminated

24:10.516 --> 24:12.151 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
the virus.

24:12.184 --> 24:15.220 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MILES O'BRIEN: This is why Fauci
and others
are optimistic they have a found
a way to

24:15.254 --> 24:21.927 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
stop Ebola its tracks. The human
body can
create the antibodies to fight
off Ebola,

24:21.960 --> 24:24.330 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
but usually not fast enough.

24:24.363 --> 24:29.802 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
An effective vaccine creates an
army of Ebola
antibodies that can stop the
virus before

24:29.835 --> 24:33.872 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
it stampedes through the body.
But here is
the ironic rub.

24:33.906 --> 24:35.674 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DR. THOMAS FRIEDEN, Director,
Centers for
Disease Control and Prevention:
If we are

24:35.708 --> 24:40.612 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
