we won't
be successful in determining
whether the vaccines

24:40.646 --> 24:42.715 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
are effective at preventing
Ebola.

24:42.748 --> 24:50.723 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MILES O'BRIEN: Dr. Tom Frieden
is director
of the CDC. Ebola cases in
Liberia are now

24:50.756 --> 24:54.326 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
