evidence.

25:01.934 --> 25:05.637 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DR. THOMAS FRIEDEN: So, the
trials under way
now will at least tell us
whether they're

25:05.671 --> 25:09.708 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
safe, and they will tell us
