difficult
for executives like myself to
actually safeguard

29:51.690 --> 29:53.792 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
the privacy of our customers.

29:53.825 --> 29:58.597 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
In the past, we have been able
to rely on
our privacy policies to create
trust with

29:58.630 --> 30:05.303 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
our customers. We can say the
privacy policy
says that we can't share your
data with third

30:05.337 --> 30:11.476 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
